---
description: JSON Schema 2020-12 and JSON-only data interchange
globs: src/tools/**/schema.json,data/**/*.json,src/core/validator.ts,scripts/validate-schemas.js
alwaysApply: true
---

# Schema + data lock

- Every schema `$schema` must be `https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema`.
- Validate with `src/core/validator.ts` (Ajv 2020-12 dialect) and `scripts/validate-schemas.js`.
- Persist and exchange **JSON text only** — no protobuf/MessagePack/CBOR/binary.
